<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="8050" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="8050">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="8050">
The number of species recognised in the 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Chrysis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Chrysis ignita" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="8050" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ignita">Chrysis ignita</taxonomicName>
group has varied from author to author. 
<bibRefCitation author="Soon, V." journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="8050" pagination="301 - 330" title="Testing the validity of Northern European species in the Chrysisignita species group (Hymenoptera: Chrysididae) with DNA Barcoding" volume="3786" year="2014">Soon et al. (2014)</bibRefCitation>
analysed species limits and found there to be 15 described European species plus cryptic species, a result more in line with 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Morgan’s">Morgan's</normalizedToken>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Morgan, D." journalOrPublisher="Handbooks for the Identification of British Insects" pageId="0" pageNumber="8050" pagination="1 - 37" title="Cuckoo-wasps. Hymenoptera, Chrysididae" volume="6 Part 5" year="1984">Morgan 1984</bibRefCitation>
) recognition of multiple species than, for example, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kunz’s">Kunz's</normalizedToken>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Kunz, P. X." journalOrPublisher="Beihefte zu den Veroeffentlichungen uer Naturschutz und Landschaftspflege in Baden-Wuerttemberg" pageId="0" pageNumber="8050" pagination="1 - 188" title="Kunz, P. X. 1994. Die Goldwespen (Chrysididae) Baden-Wurttembergs. Taxonomie, Bestimmung, Verbreitung, Kartierung und Okologie - mit einem Bestimmungsschlussel fur die deutschen Arten" volume="77" year="1994">Kunz 1994</bibRefCitation>
) much more conservative treatment.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
